      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Al Fazal Bin Shazan, and Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan, from Al A’la, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The divorced woman can perform Hajj, and testify for the rights’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "13. Muhammad ibn ’Isma‘il has narrated from al-Fadl ibn Shadhan and Abu Ali al-Ash‘ariy has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Abd al- Jabbar from Safwan from al-‘Ala’ from Muhammad ibn Muslim who has said the following: “He (the Imam), ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘A divorced woman can perform al-Hajj and testify about rights.’” "
        ]
      }
